---

## 🧠 Smart Contracts

| Contract                  | Description                                      |
|---------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| **BBCToken**              | Main token contract with pause and slippage control. |
| **BBCGuard**              | Performs buybacks, pauses during dumps.          |
| **BBCRewardDistributor**  | Daily emission system with configurable caps.     |
| **BBCAIAutonomousArbitrage** | AI arbitrage bot across multiple DEXs.         |
| **MockPool**              | Flash loan testing/utility pool.                 |

---

## 🔧 Use Cases

- **DEX Trading Pair** – BBC is tradable on Uniswap V2.
- **Yield Distribution** – Token rewards via Distributor contract.
- **Buybacks** – ETH-funded price floor protection.
- **Arbitrage** – Flash-loan and AI-powered cross-DEX arbitrage.

---

## 🔒 Security

- OpenZeppelin v5.3+ contracts used throughout.
- Slippage & circuit breakers reduce exploit vectors.
- Contract ownership protected and upgrade-ready.

---

